      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What if AI could predict WHERE you'll fail\nBEFORE it happens — and tell you HOW to fix it?\n\nNobody owns the space between:\n\"Your code has a bug\" (pre-prod AI)\n\"Your service is down\" (observability)\n\"Run a chaos experiment\" (infra layer)\n\nThis is unexplored territory.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10
    },

